From hpages at fhcrc.org  Thu Nov  3 19:19:11 2011
From: hpages at fhcrc.org (=?ISO-8859-1?Q?Herv=E9_Pag=E8s?=)
Date: Thu, 3 Nov 2011 11:19:11 -0700
Subject: [Bioc-devel] naming of TxDb packages
